    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "LIN Button Manager"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/SWC_LINButton_manager/image-2024-8-20_15-10-0-1.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/SWC_LINButton_manager/image-2024-8-20_15-10-0-1.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "headers": [
        "Index",
        "Mode",
        "State",
        "Condition",
        "Action"
      ],
      "rows": [
        [
          "1",
          "Switch Released",
          "RELEASED_EVENT",
          "按键被释放 && 上一次按键是被按下",
          "向HMI模块上报RELEASED_EVENT事件"
        ],
        [
          "2",
          "Switch Pressed",
          "EDGE_EVENT",
          "按键被按下",
          ""
        ],
        [
          "3",
          "SHORT_EVENT",
          "按键被按下 && 持续时间大于等于short event duration (250ms)",
          "向HMI模块上报SHORT_EVENT事件 && 切换到下一个“MEDIUM_EVENT”事件检测"
        ],
        [
          "4",
          "MEDIUM_EVENT",
          "按键被按下 && 持续时间大于等于medium event duration(500ms)",
          "向HMI模块上报MEDIUM_EVENT事件 && 切换到下一个“LONG_EVENT”事件检测"
        ],
        [
          "5",
          "LONG_EVENT",
          "按键被按下 && 持续时间大于等于long event duration(1250ms)",
          "向HMI模块上报LONG_EVENT事件 && 切换到下一个“EXTRALONG_EVENT”事件检测"
        ],
        [
          "6",
          "EXTRALONG_EVENT",
          "按键被按下 && 持续时间大于等于exceed long event duration(4000ms)",
          "向HMI模块上报EXTRALONG_EVENT事件"
        ]
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Question 1 : 进入到每个xxx_Event都会调用一次Rte_Call_HMIC_HMIUpdateIndication接口更新当前的Hardkey值，也就是说，如果一直接收到一个按键被被按下的信号（粘滞故障的时候），会把xxx_EDGE → xxx_EXTRALONG_EVENT依次都更新一遍给依赖模块？"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "如果LIN 按键信号一直有效，依次向HMI发送事件 EDGE_EVENT， SHORT_EVENT， MEDIUM_EVENT， LONG_EVENT， EXTRALONG_EVENT"
    },
