        [
          "1",
          "Rte_Call_HMIC_HMIUpdateIndication",
          "SWC_HMI_EngineInterface",
          "Note : 滚轮（Thumb wheel）信号处理后的值使用这个接口更新给SWC_HMI_EngineInterface模块，但是，滚轮功能都被屏蔽了。 Question 2 : 这个接口的每个参数的含义是什么？"
        ],
        [
          "2",
          "Rte_Call_HMIC_HMIQueueEvent",
          "SWC_HMI_EngineInterface",
          "Question 3: 这个接口的每个参数的含义是什么？ Question 4 : What is meanse of \"FU_SYSTEM_STATE\" and \"FU_DIC_SWITCH\" Question 5 : Where does the enumeration value definition of \"FU_SYSTEM_STATE\" and \"FU_DIC_SWITCH\" come from ？ Question 6 : Rte_Call_HMIC_HMIUpdateIndication和Rte_Call_HMIC_HMIQueueEvent有啥区别，为什么滚轮（Thumb wheel）信号用Rte_Call_HMIC_HMIUpdateIndication更新，而按键（Button）用Rte_Call_HMIC_HMIQueueEvent更新？"
        ],
        [
