    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Note : There are many rx and tx port in Davinci tools and \"Rte_SWC_LINButton_manager.h\", but just used above ports in source code."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Question 7 : SWC_LINButton_manager模块和SWC_HMI_EngineInterface模块间约定的信号、通道等协议在哪里定义的？后面增删功能的时候如何操作？"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Rte_Call_HMIC_HMIQueueEvent ( arg1 , arg2 )"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "参数："
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "arg1 ：FUID"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "arg2：Event _Id"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "两参数定义来自这个文档 FU_HMI_List_PATAC_C184.2.0_20260203.xlsx"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "#define FU_SYSTEM_STATE (177)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "#define FU_DIC_SWITCH ( 191 )"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "SWC Lin button 使用了两个FUID（ FU_SYSTEM_STATE，FU_DIC_SWITCH 每个按键都有独立的FUID 和 EVENT ID 都定义在FU_HMI_List_PATAC_C184.2.0_20260203.xlsx文档中。"
    },
